reviewText:
IF YOU WANT TO SIT AND WATCH A LECTURE ABOUT THE TIME BEFORE ATLANTIS, THEN THIS IS FOR YOU. I DONT! IF I WANT
TO SIT THROUGH A LECTURE I WOULD GO BACK TO UNIVERSITY. I DONT PAY GOOD MONEY TO HEAR A LECTURE. THE
DISCRIPTION OF THE DVD SHOULD ADVISE ALL PERTINENT INFORMATION SO THAT AN EDUCATED DECISION CAN BE MADE.
ALWAYS CHECK THE NAME OF THE STUDIO WHO MADE THE DVD, IF YOU DON T KNOW THEM DON'T BUY IT.
